title: Wes Bergmann on His ‘All Stars 3’ Win and His Place in ‘The Challenge’ Universe | Death, Taxes, and Bananas
description:
The one, the only Wes Bergmann joins Johnny today to celebrate his win on ‘The Challenge: All Stars’ Season 3. They get into his feud with Yes Duffy, the differences between ‘All Stars’ and the flagship show, what he thinks of ‘The Challenge: USA,’ his place in 'The Challenge’ universe, and a whole lot more.
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guest: Wes Bergmann
Producer: Sasha Ashall
